itemDescription: Anglo-Irish rower, barrister, politician and Lord of Appeal in Ordinary (1830-1913)

wikipedia_page.main: Edward Macnaghten, Baron Macnaghten,  (3 February 1830 – 17 February 1913) was an Anglo-Irish law lord, barrister, rower, and Conservative-Unionist politician.
